cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a framework for domain adaptation using graph embedding and neural networks. This involves techniques from machine learning, computer vision, and natural language processing, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.NE. Among these, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories as the paper deals with deep learning and image-related tasks.
